user.biography:
Oh, to be a mad, mouthy, majestic woman 
in a world full of frauds and followers…

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Brittany Renner in Los Angeles, California with @maxiejofficial, and @ellaelisque. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'SEP 02 9PM -2:00AM ELLAÉ LISQUÉ COLLECTION' Brittang Renner MODEL FOR TICKETS VISIT: E RED CARPET OPEN BAR (9-11PM) SHOPPING & MORE ellaelisque.com/fashionshow 618 S. SPRING ST. LOS ANGELES. ca 90014 THE EXCHANGE'.

node.text: I’ll be walking in @ellaelisque’s Fashion Show this Thursday 💃🏽 It also turns into an after party so it’s about to be LIT! Special thanks to @maxiejofficial for having me on the roster 🔥
